ENGINEERING REQUIREMENTS

Copilot must always:

Use Next.js 14 App Router

Server actions where appropriate

API routes

Clean file structure

Use TypeScript everywhere

Strict types.

Use Mongoose for models

No untyped schemas.

Use Tailwind CSS

Clean, minimal class usage. No bloat.

Use AWS S3 for uploads

Signed URLs, secure, validated.

Use Google Maps API

Autocomplete + Map view.

Use OpenAI API

AI enhancement endpoint for titles, descriptions, SEO text.

Use Best Practices

Modular architecture

Reusable components

Error boundaries

Input validation

Try/catch on all API routes

Proper loading + empty states

